Package arcade.potts.agent.cell

Class PottsCellContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.potts.agent.cell.PottsCellContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CellContainer
    public final class PottsCellContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements CellContainer
    Implementation of CellContainer for PottsCell agents.

    The container can be instantiated for cells with or without regions. Cell parameters are drawn from the associated PottsCellFactory instance for the given population.
